{"tid":2009198,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警身藏冰毒及偉哥返港遭海關揭發 求情指因工受傷吸毒止痛","createTime":"2020-05-09T14:36:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T05:01:25.000Z","uid":2076,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"818a5d6265da9464d95c57d95f02047b3ddc9fd9","tid":2009198,"uid":2076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T14:36:42.000Z","msg":"September 2019<br />\n原來早有前科<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190920/large/1568969781_a3b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190920%2Flarge%2F1568969781_a3b3.jpg&h=b59d4af9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【新增動新聞】<br />\n休班男警由羅湖返港時，遭本港海關揭發身藏冰毒，另管有壯陽藥「偉哥」，以及未完稅香煙。他今在粉嶺裁判法院承認藏毒等四罪，辯方求情指，被告三年前因工受傷，惟醫生處方的止痛藥卻無效，故在朋友建議下吸毒止痛。裁判官押後判刑，為被告索取感化報告，並強調不會因為他的職業而有所偏袒。<br />\n報稱警員的被告馬道宸（47歲），承認管有危險藥物、未按照入口許可證而輸入禁運物品、管有應課稅品、未有向海關人員申報共四罪。控罪指他於今年4月8日在羅湖管制站海關入境大堂某房間內，藏有0.09克冰毒、玻璃管、膠管及開口膠樽、一粒內含屬第一類毒品「昔多芬」的「偉哥」；另藏有238支未完稅香煙，而未有向海關人員申報該些香煙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20190920/HXKC4BVU3BTR3ZFR7H7VGUQYXA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190920%2FHXKC4BVU3BTR3ZFR7H7VGUQYXA%2F&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpdekL701Gi2Y7kfdl15EDb4%3D&h=e1b75ea8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20190920%2FHXKC4BVU3BTR3ZFR7H7VGUQYXA%2F&h=0d341195\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20190920/HXKC4BVU3BTR3ZFR7H7VGUQYXA/</a>"},{"pid":"b217aaca897aa6c5edac71a2b8fd5f54743d3c67","tid":2009198,"uid":321977,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T14:38:38.000Z","msg":"吸毒止痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小學雞呃9老師級數嘅理由"},{"pid":"a8a86aa866826bea742adf8625beda83a8e1988a","tid":2009198,"uid":2076,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b217aaca897aa6c5edac71a2b8fd5f54743d3c67","tid":2009198,"uid":321977,"li